parameters.name: BackupSetDataFormat
parameters.description:
The format in which the incremental backup set is downloaded. Valid values:

- **Native**

- **SQL**

- **CSV**

- **JSON**

> Default value: Native.

parameters.name: BackupSetId
parameters.description: The ID of the incremental backup task. To obtain the task ID, you can call the [DescribeIncrementBackupList](~~2869833~~) operation and view the value of the **BackupSetJobId** parameter in the response.

parameters.name: BackupSetName
parameters.description: The ID of the incremental backup set. To obtain the backup set ID, you can call the [DescribeIncrementBackupList](~~2869833~~) operation and view the value of the **BackupSetId** parameter in the response.

parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: The client token that is used to ensure the idempotence of the request.
